$$
X(N) = \dfrac{\lambda N}{1+\sigma(N-1)+\kappa N(N-1)}
$$

* $$\sigma$$, the overhead of contention
* $$\kappa$$, the overhead of crosstalk
* $$\lambda$$, how fast the system operates in ideal conditions
